OL,3,CHundreds visit saved library to
OL,4,Cexperience maths and nature
OL,6,FNearly 600 people visited a Scottish
OL,7,FBorders museum that was previously
OL,8,Funder threat of closure during Maths
OL,9,FWeek Scotland.
OL,11,FHawick Museum, whose future was
OL,12,Fsecured earlier this month, hosted
OL,13,Ffamilies, schools and community groups
OL,14,Ffor a programme which explored the
OL,15,Frole of maths in nature.
OL,17,FVisitor numbers exceeded expectations,
OL,18,Fwith 38 per cent more people attending
OL,19,Fthan the target.
