OL,6,F179 children and their families took
OL,7,Fpart in Family Fun Day activities,
OL,8,Fwhile early years sessions introduced
OL,9,Fpre-schoolers to mathematics through
OL,10,Fstorytelling and games.
OL,12,FSchoolchildren, meanwhile, were kept
OL,13,Fentertained with author book-signing
OL,14,Fevents, storytelling and singing.
