OL,3,CHundreds visit saved library to
OL,4,Cexperience maths and nature
OL,6,FEmily Moir, Live Borders education
OL,7,Fofficer at Hawick Museum, said: "Maths
OL,8,FWeek Scotland gave us the chance to
OL,9,Fshow how mathematics is all around us
OL,10,F` in the trees, the seasons, the
OL,11,Fwildlife, and even in the shadows we
OL,12,Fcast.
OL,14,F"By making maths playful and hands-on,
OL,15,Fwe've helped break down barriers and
OL,16,Finspire children and adults alike to
OL,17,Fsee the subject in a new light."
